{"tid":1828737,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"知法犯法，繼續謀殺 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-01-18T06:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T06:26:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5c75cb352e0ca5ec396d714c2d0c1c7ed06a3b50","tid":1828737,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:07:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200118/20845672/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200118%2F20845672%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKNKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=04cb6d87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200118%2F20845672%2F&h=12e2899b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200118/20845672/</a><br />\n<br />\n知法犯法，繼續謀殺 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200118/large/1579255635_d95e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200118%2Flarge%2F1579255635_d95e.jpg&h=cac7e327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒娥出席答問大會，民主派議員提問時，多人要求她下台，斥為「賣港賊」、質問作為天主教徒的她心中有無良知公義、幾時落地獄&hellip;&hellip;統統拒回應。粵俗形容人「針拮都冇滴血」，就是這類行屍走肉。<br />\n<br />\n即使動用百億公帑，推出10大紓困措施，都是口惠而實不至，無確實時間表等同虛擬，這些贖罪券掩口費如何服眾平息民憤？要港人自己出錢來掩自己的口？真荒謬，別中計。一邊偽善一邊縱容黑警濫捕、濫暴，甚至考慮在抗爭活動中使用電槍等可致命電擊武器，以期迅速制服。如今的警棍胡椒噴霧各式子彈真槍實彈&hellip;&hellip;都用上了，逾7,000人被捕，年齡最小11歲，無數人失蹤或送中，仍未滿意？趕盡殺絕？<br />\n<br />\n企圖收買人心卻又姑息養奸？真是個精神分裂的政府。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大家看到油塘紀律部隊宿舍，一名卅多歲男子從高處墮下死亡片段，怵目驚心，明明是（昏迷或死亡）失去意識無知覺者，在後樓梯狹窄氣窗被人推下，無可疑？天網恢恢疏而不漏，幸有外傭姐姐隔窗無意拍下放上網廣傳，罪證有目共睹。以前所有「被自殺」的死者（周梓樂、陳彥霖&hellip;&hellip;等等），冤案何時昭雪？</span><br />\n<br />\n知法犯法、繼續謀殺──黑警及一哥還有臉天天圓謊？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"c789252d60cc05c74dea2800119b3cc3f34bc4b3","tid":1828737,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"119 星期日 天下制裁 遮打花園集會安排<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1828158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1828158</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n119 星期日 天下制裁遮打花園集會<br />\n日期 : 1月19日 星期日<br />\n時間 : 1400 可以入場,  15:00 開始<br />\n地點 : 遮打花園, 遮打道, 皇后像廣場<br />\n<br />\n坐爆多人得滯就<span style=\"color: orange;\">向東邊 金鐘/銅鑼灣 方向流水式散去</span><br />\n(<span style=\"color: orange;\">所以進場朋友請盡量由中環西邊方向加入</span>, 地鐵站即中環 A/B/C/D/G/H 出口沿遮打道加入,  <span style=\"color: orange;\">請盡量避免由金鐘站加入以防互擠</span>)<br />\n<br />\n付中環地圖參考<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Zn2JVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Zn2JVB.png&h=e22d8eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n========================================<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n請<br />\n準時準時準時<br />\n坐爆坐爆坐爆<br />\n之後向金鐘銅鑼灣方向散去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}